佢</blockquote><br />\n可能唔係骨 拮新佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809cbaa9b3abc79cbe10a198ba36dba603fa1135","tid":426430,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔係要增肥，你係要增肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪認真左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪增肥之後先操肌？<br />\n每星期會跑5-6個鐘"},{"pid":"d4792123a69263351d11965c80d5a1758ae765e4","tid":426430,"uid":90045,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:22:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢去食多啲好野<br />\n又可以增肥 又可以拍拖<br />\n話晒增肥容易過減肥</blockquote><br />\n就係成日同佢食好嘢  餵到佢肥<br />\n但瘦撚真心食唔肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實女朋友好介意肥<br />\n佢話著衫唔好睇  同我企埋一齊好肥<br />\n出街影相唔滿意 會發脾氣<br />\n我就覺得幾得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d601ac0a33194226e881f8f32ea29a4b583b8b1b","tid":426430,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊一年扑野都女上男下問題即可解決</blockquote><br />\n至弊我肯佢唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話我條骨拮親佢</blockquote><br />\n可能唔係骨 拮新佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估係鳩毛喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3787dfc42417aeb70efcd59a13f5e7dce0601f7d","tid":426430,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"女朋友身型同中大Emilia差唔多<br />\n高少少均勻啲"},{"pid":"b90cb877d94326e5b4d89bb891fcbb7274b638d7","tid":426430,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友身型同中大Emilia差唔多<br />\n高少少均勻啲</blockquote><br />\n正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" cl